					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hey, thanks! A deliberate author choice here was to let the Foundation bring the SCP in disabled, but mostly intact. Any great hero franchise needs to have that sequel hook available, right? One day, we just might see&#8230;</p> <p><span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 2:</strong></span> <strong>2 Hot 2 Contain</strong></p> <p>or even&#8230;</p> <p><span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 3:</strong></span> <strong>Bigg Redd Rolls Again</strong></p> <p>e:</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Other&nbsp;Naming&nbsp;Options</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Other&nbsp;Naming&nbsp;Options&nbsp;?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 2:</strong></span> <strong>The Damn Fire Strikes Back</strong><br /> &amp;<br /> <span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 3:</strong></span> <strong>Return Of The Redd Guy</strong></p> <hr /> <p><span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 2:</strong></span> <strong>The Redd Knight</strong><br /> &amp;<br /> <span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 3:</strong></span> <strong>Mennace Rises</strong></p> <hr /> <p><span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 2:</strong></span> <strong>The Redd Reloaded</strong><br /> &amp;<br /> <span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 3:</strong></span> <strong>Redd-volutions</strong></p> <hr /> <p><span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 2:</strong></span> <strong>The Two Fires</strong><br /> &amp;<br /> <span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 3:</strong></span> <strong>Return Of The Singe</strong></p> <hr /> <p><span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 2:</strong></span> <strong>The Curse Of The Redd Pearl</strong><br /> &amp;<br /> <span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 3:</strong></span> <strong>Redd Man's Chest</strong><br /> &amp;<br /> <span style="color: red"><strong>Redd Mennace 4:</strong></span> <strong>At Fire's End</strong></p> </div> </div> </div> 
