					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12828020#post-4431069</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12828020/scp-4601#post-4431069</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2019 05:53:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Nickthebrick1</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5208936</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hey guys, this is a collab project between me and Boogey, we wanted to showcase the stereotypes of the &quot;dark avengers&quot; sort of characters (I.E. Batman, Punisher etc.)</p> <p>We both wanted to play on the idea and we like the results, hope you enjoy!</p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boogey-man23" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2362395&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574663239" alt="Boogey_Man23" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2362395)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/boogey-man23" >Boogey_Man23</a></span> the one who collaborated with me. I wouldn't be able to polish it effectively without him. Thanks so much Boogey</p> <p>Thank you for all those who gave this SCP a review when it was still in a draft stage:<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simartar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5489226&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574663239" alt="Simartar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5489226)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simartar" >Simartar</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/navimaster" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5839130&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574663239" alt="Navimaster" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5839130)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/navimaster" >Navimaster</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574663239" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tuomey-tombstone" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=462110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574663239" alt="Tuomey Tombstone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=462110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tuomey-tombstone" >Tuomey Tombstone</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/francis-scalia" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=209952&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574663239" alt="Francis Scalia" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=209952)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/francis-scalia" >Francis Scalia</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fieldstone" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1436137&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1574663239" alt="fieldstone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1436137)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fieldstone" >fieldstone</a></span></p> <p>and all those who gave a look at it. If I forgot a name, just let me know.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12828020#post-4431060</guid>
				<title>Co-Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12828020/scp-4601#post-4431060</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2019 05:37:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Boogey_Man23</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2362395</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p>Bigg Redd, Bigg Redd,<br /> Puts out flames before they spread!<br /> If there's a fire, you're in luck,<br /> He's a living firetruck!</p> <p>Look out! Here comes the skip <strong><span style="color: red">Bigg Redd!</span></strong></p> </blockquote> </div> <p>Thanks very much to:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simartar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5489226&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609316879" alt="Simartar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5489226)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simartar" >Simartar</a></span>, who reviewed this draft at several stages in its development.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/francis-scalia" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=209952&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609316879" alt="Francis Scalia" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=209952)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/francis-scalia" >Francis Scalia</a></span>, whose comment on the original version of this SCP helped guide the shape of this new version of the article. To everybody else who read and gave input on that original version as well.</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/navimaster" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5839130&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609316879" alt="Navimaster" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5839130)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/navimaster" >Navimaster</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609316879" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tuomey-tombstone" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=462110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609316879" alt="Tuomey Tombstone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=462110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tuomey-tombstone" >Tuomey Tombstone</a></span>, <span class="error-inline"><em>fortunefavorsbold</em> does not match any existing user name</span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kleptocracynow" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4875396&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609316879" alt="KleptocracyNow" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4875396)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kleptocracynow" >KleptocracyNow</a></span> - who all read in chat and gave feedback. Also anyone else who might have read this draft that I didn't mention.</li> <li>Of course, my co-author <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nickthebrick1" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5208936&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609316879" alt="Nickthebrick1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5208936)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nickthebrick1" >Nickthebrick1</a></span> who was a dedicated worker and a great collaborative partner!</li> </ul> <p>And thanks, as always, to you the reader. I hope this article is entertaining!</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Image&nbsp;Credit</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfol